  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1303342/" class="title-link">世界大，生命长</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1303342"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/mumudancing/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1553180-94.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/mumudancing/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">mumudancing</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2008-02-13"
      class="main-meta">2008-02-13 21:11:32</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1303342_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  约700页南怀瑾《庄子諵譁》读毕，深呼一口气。   每个人都知道，庄开篇就说北冥有鱼，逍遥游啊游，就以为通篇都说这个鱼怎么变成鸟，怎么飞得远飞得高飞到世界以外。 其实呢，鬼知道他最后讲了个冷笑话，八竿子打不着这条big fish。   说，南极有个帝，北极有个帝，他们到天地...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1303342/#comments">(39回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">70有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
